data.description: This one of a kind property is here for you..If you’ve ever been waiting to purchase a log cabin, the time is now right. This luxurious open concept log cabin has a matching drive through 30 x 40 four car garage. As if that’s not enough, a smaller, matching two car garage already set up for dog kennel is located next to it.  Become welcomed with a wraparound porch, that entices you to spend your evenings, swinging and enjoying the crickets. As you enter, you engulf the beauty of the kitchen and all its custom cabinetry, granite countertops and all NEW NEW NEW appliances. The open living room shows off the stone fireplace and windows windows windows. This prestige home is located on 1.85 flat acreage. Never lose power in any storm, with a 24K Generac system.  This beauty is centrally located near I 70.  Don’t let this one slip away. Schedule your private showing today.
